1
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:02,750
I finally caught you.

2
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:05,110
Cut it out. We're at work.

3
00:00:05,550 --> 00:00:07,550
What if someone sees us?

4
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:10,640
Are you avoiding me?

5
00:00:12,010 --> 00:00:13,100
No, I'm not.

6
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:14,510
Yes, you are.

7
00:00:14,510 --> 00:00:15,640
Why?

8
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:19,520
That's because...

9
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:27,400
Are they telling you to get back?

10
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:30,700
Yeah...

11
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:33,700
Sorry.

12
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,790
I have to get back to the set.

13
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:41,370
See you later.

14
00:00:49,260 --> 00:00:51,590
Seriously, what is going on?

15
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:55,890
Huh? What?

16
00:00:56,770 --> 00:00:57,930
Like I said!

17
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:01,770
Makoto's manager
told us to break up.

18
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,200
And then? He pinned you to the wall?

19
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:06,780
What's going on?

20
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,610
Yeah, I don't get it either.

21
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:14,700
The manager said Makoto agreed to it too.

22
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:17,490
But he's acting weird today.

23
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:19,750
Did you ask him directly?

24
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:21,160
How could I ask him that?

25
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,790
Ask him if he wants to break up?

26
00:01:23,170 --> 00:01:24,670
Do you want to break up, then?

27
00:01:26,130 --> 00:01:27,550
No.

28
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:30,970
But...

29
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:34,110
I understand where the manager is coming from, too.

30
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,140
I...

31
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,770
I can't hold him back.

32
00:01:39,930 --> 00:01:40,980
You're unbelievable.

33
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:43,480
Fine, I'll ask him for you.

34
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,440
What?

35
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,480
I'm hanging up now.

36
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:48,320
Hey! Wait! Natsu!?
